name: The Journey of Sinta - Mount Fuji
description:
Sinta is a simple girl who has big dreams. Her dream is to travel the world.
Currently, Sinta has arrived in Japan and she’s stopping at the village of Iyashi no Sato which is at the foot of Mount Fuji.
At one of the restaurants in the village of Iyashi no Sato, Sinta met a small robot named Gin. They made friends and Gin started invites Sinta around the village.
For a while, Sinta stayed in the village and then continued her journey to other countries.
